            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>arborio&nbsp;</strong><strong>rice</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 sec, stirring to coat the grains in oil</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>S</strong><strong><strong>haoxing</strong> wine</strong> and cook for a further 30 sec or until it has&nbsp;almost evaporated</p>\r\n<p>Add 1/3 of the <strong>stock</strong>&nbsp;with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once absorbed, continue to add the <strong>stock</strong>, a little at a time, stirring almost constantly until the stock has absorbed and the rice is cooked&nbsp;</p>",
